Attended ‘National unity campaign’ on abrogation of articles 370 and 35A. Chief guest is union minister Sh Dharmendra Pradhan ji and Special guest is Jammu and Kashmir former DGP Sh Rajendra kumar ji.He belongs to Nizamabad.
